{"tid":349650,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有咩方法可以踢走個on9 housemate?","createTime":"2017-08-06T16:14:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-06T19:34:17.000Z","uid":133140,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5cde12e9dc47e5fe7ca54879501607b098c5740a","tid":349650,"uid":133140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T16:14:04.000Z","msg":"代Fd開po<br />\n<br />\n話說係外國讀u 今年識左條友就諗住下年一齊夾錢租屋住<br />\n睇左幾間屋之後搵到一間我地都幾鍾意 所以睇完冇耐就簽左約<br />\n個屋主就話要我地一租就租成年 同埋要係搬入去前交哂租<br />\n間屋就10990 HKD 一個月 咁十二個月就131880 HKD 一人一半就10990 x 6 = 65940 HKD 仲有另外要比9990 HKD 訂金 個陣我係夠錢即時比自己既屋租 佢就冇錢比 因為個屋主講左 話如果佢搬入去入前比唔到佢個份既屋租 就會沒收左個訂金 我比左既租就可以比番我 所以我就比左自己份租 佢媽就比左個訂金(反正到最後都拎得番 如果有整爛野我會比番錢)<br />\n咁本身都知佢屋企唔係特別有錢 相比起其他屋 都知依間係貴 <br />\n個陣我都有同佢講過要唔要搵其他屋住 因為佢係Uk citizen就拎開student finance 屋企又係拎綜援 佢屋企既收入來源唔計佢自己 就得佢個家姐<br />\n但佢就死要面咁話一定要住依間 自己番開酒吧既工 人工唔係特別高 但都話最多自己番工草錢 暑假番full time 我計過佢就算每日番足8個鐘 當佢完全0開支 佢都冇可能係搬入去之前草夠錢 佢之前又講埋啲咩 唔夠就問親戚借<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n開頭同佢都好地地 慢慢就發現佢愈黎愈on9 平時唔撚聽人講野都算 仲要係人地背後做埋啲小動作 撩事鬥非 又挑撥離間 淨係識作鳩埋啲故仔吹水又剩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 搞到我地玩開個堆既人都覺得佢好煩<br />\n一開始第一次我就同佢講 話不如我比番一半既訂金佢媽 我就同個屋主講叫佢比番我份租我 同佢講我唔想同佢一齊住 怕尷尬個啲 但佢自己唔覺得會尷尬 又話自己實夠錢比 話比2個選擇我 一係就照扮冇野 照同啲fd出去玩 番學個啲 做番朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一係就大家唔理大家 自己做自己野 我話你搞咁撚多野出黎 唔係覺得仲有fd做嘛？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢又話 最多下年係間屋到set啲規矩 我就覺得佢on99 所以就直接搵佢老母傾 反正個訂金啲錢係佢老母比既<br />\n咁我就搵佢老母傾 佢老母就話鳩番我轉頭 話人地都唔覺得尷尬 得我一個覺得尷尬 講到係我麻鳩煩咁 我講埋我會比番一半訂金 佢老母又唔理我 叫我同佢住 反正佢讀最後一年 叫我做佢朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 話佢需要人睇住佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 依家佢好忙日日番工好辛苦草錢 叫我唔好比多樣野佢煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n過左排我再搵番佢同佢傾 話聽佢老母講佢要好辛苦番工搵錢 比我拎番啲屋租 各自去搵新屋好過 佢就忽然間同我講 話我係咪暗示佢冇錢比 事實上自己已經有錢比 只係想留到9月搬入去先比 我心諗你都on99 有冇人會有錢比唔依家比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我問佢點解唔依家比 佢就吹到話因爲同屋主講左搬入去個日先比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點知轉個頭就佢自己柒 佢自己cap圖po snapchat 有個email係講政府比佢既錢 本身等5個工作天就收到 話自己等撚左5個禮拜都未收到 <br />\n有幾個fd係Facebook 叫佢出去飲杯野 都話自己冇錢 日日係屋企鳩fing fing 等老母煮埋野比佢食 係屋企打ps4 <br />\n最on9係條友成日話自己有錢 只係唔岩啲錢黎得太遲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 姐係佢個student finance 係隔一排先比佢 啲錢係政府借比佢 到佢畢左業咪又係要還番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  係到洗撚埋哂啲錢去買酒飲買毒品買大麻食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家點算好 有冇咩方法可以甩到身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我個陣真係唔知會搞到咁複雜 驚佢high大左個陣斬鳩我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49abb14a7d8867eb2741765f4298553edbcb720b","tid":349650,"uid":35445,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T16:16:00.000Z","msg":"不如你都係加返標點，分好d段落再post過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d056784a768c36167135326c89b4e281a011a23","tid":349650,"uid":36077,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T16:16:46.000Z","msg":"好撚長&hellip;"},{"pid":"ab863739704c44c3e9e17b8657bfba62bae8f7d7","tid":349650,"uid":62514,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T16:17:15.000Z","msg":"好撚長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"686a6ad26fc8ac4fbcda0b0ac549db37d31141cc","tid":349650,"uid":50818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T16:18:20.000Z","msg":"too long can't read"},{"pid":"704b61d8266dcd794d617d49233cf7facb4d6edd","tid":349650,"uid":133140,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T16:28:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>代Fd開po<br />\n<br />\n話說係外國讀u，今年識左條友就諗住下年一齊夾錢租屋住。睇左幾間屋之後搵到一間我地都幾鍾意，所以睇完冇耐就簽左約。個屋主就話要我地一租就租成年，同埋要係搬入去前交哂租。間屋就10990 HKD 一個月，咁十二個月就131880 HKD，一人一半就10990 x 6 = 65940 HKD，仲有另外要比9990 HKD 訂金。個陣我係夠錢即時比自己既屋租，佢就冇錢比。因為個屋主講左，話如果佢搬入去入前比唔到佢個份既屋租，就會沒收左個訂金，我比左既租就可以比番我，所以我就比左自己份租 佢媽就比左個訂金。(反正到最後都拎得番 如果有整爛野我會比番錢)<br />\n<br />\n咁本身都知佢屋企唔係特別有錢，相比起其他屋都知依間係貴。個陣我都有同佢講過要唔要搵其他屋住，因為佢係Uk citizen就拎開student finance，屋企又係拎綜援，佢屋企既收入來源唔計佢自己，就得佢個家姐。但佢就死要面咁話一定要住依間，自己番開酒吧既工，人工唔係特別高，但都話最多自己番工草錢，暑假番full time。我計過佢就算每日番足8個鐘，當佢完全0開支，佢都冇可能係搬入去之前草夠錢。佢之前又講埋啲咩，唔夠就問親戚借<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n開頭同佢都好地地，慢慢就發現佢愈黎愈on9。平時唔撚聽人講野都算，仲要係人地背後做埋啲小動作，撩事鬥非，又挑撥離間，淨係識作鳩埋啲故仔吹水又剩。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 搞到我地玩開個堆既人都覺得佢好煩。<br />\n<br />\n一開始第一次我就同佢講，話不如我比番一半既訂金佢媽，我就同個屋主講叫佢比番我份租我，同佢講我唔想同佢一齊住，怕尷尬個啲。但佢自己唔覺得會尷尬，又話自己實夠錢比，仲比2個選擇我：一係就照扮冇野，照同啲fd出去玩，番學個啲，做番朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一係就大家唔理大家，自己做自己野。我話你搞咁撚多野出黎，唔係覺得仲有fd做嘛？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢又話最多下年係間屋到set啲規矩。我就覺得佢on99所以就直接搵佢老母傾，反正個訂金啲錢係佢老母比既。<br />\n<br />\n咁我就搵佢老母傾，佢老母就話鳩番我轉頭，話人地都唔覺得尷尬，得我一個覺得尷尬，講到係我麻鳩煩咁。我講埋我會比番一半訂金，佢老母又唔理我，叫我同佢住，反正佢讀最後一年，叫我做佢朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，話佢需要人睇住佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。仲話依家佢好忙日日番工好辛苦草錢，叫我唔好比多樣野佢煩。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n過左排我再搵番佢同佢傾，話聽佢老母講佢要好辛苦番工搵錢，比我拎番啲屋租，各自去搵新屋好過。佢就忽然間同我講話我係咪暗示佢冇錢比，事實上自己已經有錢比，只係想留到9月搬入去先比。我心諗你都on99，有冇人會有錢比唔依家比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我問佢點解唔依家比，佢就吹到話因爲同屋主講左搬入去個日先比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點知轉個頭就佢自己柒，佢自己cap圖po snapchat 有個email係講政府比佢既錢，本身等5個工作天就收到，話自己等撚左5個禮拜都未收到。<br />\n <br />\n有幾個fd係Facebook 叫佢出去飲杯野，都話自己冇錢，日日係屋企鳩fing fing 等老母煮埋野比佢食，係屋企打ps4 。<br />\n<br />\n最on9係條友成日話自己有錢，只係唔岩啲錢黎得太遲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 姐係佢個student finance 係隔一排先比佢 啲錢係政府借比佢，到佢畢左業咪又係要還番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  係到洗撚埋哂啲錢去買酒飲買毒品買大麻食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n依家點算好，有冇咩方法可以甩到身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我個陣真係唔知會搞到咁複雜，驚佢high大左個陣斬鳩我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nSor9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 直接copy左個fd段野up上黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62fd6eba681bbf99fca24696fb35209c53d9c195","tid":349650,"uid":71826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T16:41:05.000Z","msg":"喺外國讀書果然中文唔合格"},{"pid":"9073700af83513871de54394e7311d6b227fdf7b","tid":349650,"uid":133140,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T16:44:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>喺外國讀書果然中文唔合格</blockquote><br />\n合格就唔洗去外國讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd48442eaeb61610e599da5031f626eed2540381","tid":349650,"uid":57488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T16:50:04.000Z","msg":"睇完都唔係好覺佢on9係邊度"},{"pid":"f9964a687ae99d3a2ac82d86b9e5b5f9e468ef54","tid":349650,"uid":49055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T16:50:38.000Z","msg":"好撚貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3de3be1fe6e28c22bdddbc9a45392cc407c7ec7","tid":349650,"uid":133140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T16:57:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇完都唔係好覺佢on9係邊度</blockquote><br />\n係佢做啲野好on9，開埋佢同佢媽講野又講到1999咁，話係我個fd想自己獨佔成間屋。但明明係我個fd同佢講話比番一半訂金佢，等我個fd可以拎番啲屋租。佢自己有好多fd都未搵到屋，佢大可以搵人頂左我個fd個位，但佢唔想就係因為想繼續痴番埋堆fd到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22c139e28baf5bfa963395ab697ad6216fac072a","tid":349650,"uid":71826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T17:04:09.000Z","msg":"10句總結晒全部 ok?"},{"pid":"8906f29dfa836fd7cb91dc750fd9715c25f90ad1","tid":349650,"uid":115104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T17:10:28.000Z","msg":"1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b51993367a99521fb35d21c76eec84d3dae4998d","tid":349650,"uid":48113,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T17:27:18.000Z","msg":"朋友拎綜緩但外國讀書？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"473742e78d85f0118eb740cad0c0c47c7a300434","tid":349650,"uid":822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T17:53:17.000Z","msg":"你住倫敦？d租都幾貴下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你知你個fd無錢就揾平d嘅屋ma,咪同佢住啦，自己住好過啦<br />\n利申：過來人"},{"pid":"eaae21976ac25783ad19944ff7541da07eefb8ef","tid":349650,"uid":133140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T18:00:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>朋友拎綜緩但外國讀書？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有英國國籍個個，姐係冇錢交租個個先係英國拎綜援個個，唔係我個朋友。"},{"pid":"023ac5e8e9368fa3acda0ef87c44405f6828ec24","tid":349650,"uid":133140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T18:03:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你住倫敦？d租都幾貴下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你知你個fd無錢就揾平d嘅屋ma,咪同佢住啦，自己住好過啦<br />\n利申：過來人</blockquote><br />\n問題係佢要我個朋友比番哂個訂金佢老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我朋友就係想拎番自比左既租金，再自己搵屋住，但依家就係唔敢直接拎番啲錢。見到佢搞到咁都覺得煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6aff1fe96d176613e71dc641255121fea2cf3d89","tid":349650,"uid":24045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T18:07:07.000Z","msg":"邊個叫你part個煩煩友，錢又無"},{"pid":"df6935f755ba15c58d3c6f8eafc24159cf4eb6fd","tid":349650,"uid":24966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T18:37:34.000Z","msg":"Btw點解一租就要租一年加比一年錢？<br />\n正常即使份約一年住夠6個月可以走只要提前兩個月通知<br />\n比錢最多都係一次比半年錢之後再同佢計<br />\n<br />\n同人夾份真係好撚麻煩<br />\n尤其是窮撚再加多要求<br />\n下下年我應該都係租個studio住算"},{"pid":"bd9a1577ce1b594b9175e5e4e196a77c4a34c88b","tid":349650,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T18:39:10.000Z","msg":"睇唔明"},{"pid":"97bf3400532a6e6bad553b709375cff9150a1337","tid":349650,"uid":105515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T19:21:57.000Z","msg":"我第一年又係識左個on9仔一齊住<br />\n第二年即"},{"pid":"9501122ae5750b2c0539ef4526b754d075e47938","tid":349650,"uid":105515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T19:23:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我第一年又係識左個on9仔一齊住<br />\n第二年即刻閃人</blockquote>"},{"pid":"9d60630f9cf3e79ea13a53265d2f24517e74a0c6","tid":349650,"uid":131955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T19:33:24.000Z","msg":"租studio 啦，同人夾呢樣個樣真係好撚煩